<p>
<a name="Introduction"></a>
<h2 class=header>Introduction</h2>
Welcome to my personal "Yurt Notes".
<p>
Check out the <b><a href="Yurt#How%20To%20Manuals">manuals</a></b> first to get an idea about the overall considerations to build a yurt. 
Additionally I wrote down some of my notes and calculations I made myself and implemented a <i>"Yurt Online Calculator"</i> based on those calculations. Also, a lots of hints I received from people I visited who also build their own yurts have been included here.
<p>
I developed my yurt (11/2005) according these notes, and I still add and edit those notes here occassionally.
<p>
<br clear=both>
<center><table class=fotoborder hspace=16 vspace=4 width=470 ><tr><td align=center><img width=470 height=464 src="Pics/yurt-details.png" class=foto ></a><br><font size=1>Yurt Parts Overview</font></td></tr></table></center>
<p>
<center>
